<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN222-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉait taṉmakaṉ piṟantapiṉ peyarttucceṉṟu pottiyār eṉakku iṭantāveṉṟu coṟṟatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN222">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>aḻalavir vayaṅkiḻaip polinta mēṉi</l>
<l>niḻaliṉum pōkāniṉ veyyōḷ payanta</l>
<l>pukaḻcāl putalvaṉ piṟantapiṉ vāveṉa</l>
<l>veṉṉiva ṇoḻitta vaṉpi lāḷa</l>
<l>veṇṇā tirukkuvai yallai</l>
<l>yeṉṉiṭam yātumaṟ ṟicaivey yōyē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="4">O loveless man who cast me off here, </l>
<l corresp="3">saiying “come” – after a praise-worthy son has been born, </l>
<l corresp="2">brought forth by her who is keen on you, not going away [from you any] more than [your] shadow, </l>
<l corresp="1">[her] body radiant with glowing jewels that shine [like] fire, </l>
<l>you won’t sit [here] without [fore]thought.</l>
<l>What is my place, you keen on fame?  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
